trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when the workflow runtime engine attempts to load a workflow instance that is currently loaded by another workflow runtime engine instance.
trans-unit.target: Unntaket oppstod når arbeidsflyten runtime databasemotoren prøver å laste inn en arbeidsflytforekomst som er lastet inn av en annen runtime motoren arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Additionally, this exception is thrown when the workflow runtime engine attempts to save a workflow after the ownership timeout that was specified while loading the workflow has expired.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg unntak denne under kjøring arbeidsflytmotoren forsøk på å lagre en arbeidsflyt etter eierskap tidsavbruddet som ble angitt under innlasting av arbeidsflyten er utløpt.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] The WorkflowOwnershipException is used by persistence services which support the capability for multiple applications to access the same database.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]WorkflowOwnershipException brukes av utholdenhet tjenester som støtter gjør mulighet for flere programmer for å få tilgang til samme database.

trans-unit.source: In such an environment, an instance of the workflow runtime may try to load a workflow that is already loaded by another instance of the workflow runtime engine.
trans-unit.target: I slike et miljø kan en forekomst av arbeidsflyten kjøretiden prøver å laste inn en arbeidsflyt som allerede er lastet inn av en annen forekomst av arbeidsflyten runtime motoren.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SQLWorkflowPersistenceService> class throws the WorkflowOwnershipException when this situation occurs.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SQLWorkflowPersistenceService>klassen oppstår WorkflowOwnershipException når dette skjer.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SQLWorkflowPersistenceService>

trans-unit.source: If you implement a persistence service that throws the WorkflowOwnershipException you should provide the <xref:System.Guid> of the workflow instance for which the exception occurs by using an appropriate constructor for the class or setting the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException.InstanceId%2A> property before you throw the exception.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du implementerer en utholdenhet-tjeneste som oppstår i WorkflowOwnershipException du må oppgi den <xref:System.Guid>til arbeidsflytforekomsten som forekommer unntaket ved hjelp av en riktig konstruktør for klassen eller innstillingen det <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException.InstanceId%2A>egenskapen før du throw unntaket.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowOwnershipException.InstanceId%2A> </xref:System.Guid>
